OL,3,C'Feels like he's still here': Tony
OL,4,CIommi honours 'dear friend' Ozzy
OL,6,FBlack Sabbath guitarist Tony Iommi has
OL,7,Fpaid tribute to his "dear friend" Ozzy
OL,8,FOsbourne on the first anniversary of
OL,9,Fhis death, adding: "I still can't
OL,10,Fbelieve that he's not with us."
OL,12,FThe singer, known as the Prince of
OL,13,FDarkness, died aged 76 in July last
OL,14,Fyear just over two weeks after his
OL,15,FBack To The Beginning farewell concert
OL,16,Fwhere he was reunited with his
OL,17,Fbandmates.
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@aO]qD@TOUrD@_O]
