OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784879327
OL,3,C'Feels like he's still here': Tony
OL,4,CIommi honours 'dear friend' Ozzy
OL,6,FOsbourne is famed for co-founding the
OL,7,Fchart-topping group in the 1960s,
OL,8,Falongside guitarist Iommi, bass player
OL,9,FTerence "Geezer" Butler and drummer
OL,10,FBill Ward.
OL,12,FIommi, 78, paid tribute to his late
OL,13,Fbandmate in a lengthy message on X on
OL,14,FWednesday, posting: "Well, it's now a
OL,15,Fyear since Ozzy's passing and I still
OL,16,Fcan't believe that he's not with us.
OL,18,F"I watch him on YouTube and it feels
OL,19,Flike he's still here with us.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@PO]vD@UOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
