PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784879327
OL,3,C'Feels like he's still here': Tony
OL,4,CIommi honours 'dear friend' Ozzy
OL,6,F"We always stayed in touch, almost
OL,7,Fevery week or so and we'd usually talk
OL,8,Fabout our ailments and then about what
OL,9,Fwe'd been doing that particular week."
OL,11,FOsbourne, who died of a reported heart
OL,12,Fattack, had suffered from a string of
OL,13,Fhealth issues over the years,
OL,14,Fincluding multiple surgeries following
OL,15,Fa fall in February 2019 and being
OL,16,Fdiagnosed with Parkinson's disease.
OL,18,FIommi, nicknamed The Godfather Of
OL,19,FHeavy Metal, was diagnosed with blood
OL,20,Fcancer in 2012 and announced he was in
OL,21,Fremission in 2016.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
