PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784879327
OL,3,C'Feels like he's still here': Tony
OL,4,CIommi honours 'dear friend' Ozzy
OL,6,FThe Grammy-winner continued: "The fans
OL,7,Fhave been absolutely brilliant and the
OL,8,Flove and respect that they have shown
OL,9,Ffor him has just been amazing.
OL,11,F"I'm so glad that we were able to play
OL,12,Fone final show with the original line
OL,13,Fup of Sabbath at the Back To The
OL,14,FBeginning show in our hometown of
OL,15,FBirmingham.
OL,17,F"There will never be another Ozzy. I
OL,18,Fmiss you my dear friend."
OL,26,@nD@^OUsD@AOUyD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
