OL,3,C'Feels like he's still here': Tony
OL,4,CIommi honours 'dear friend' Ozzy
OL,6,FOn the first anniversary of his death,
OL,7,FOzzy was also remembered by his widow
OL,8,FSharon, who encouraged fans to
OL,9,F"remember how funny he was ` funny and
OL,10,Fcharismatic and real" in an interview
OL,11,Fwith BBC Radio West Midlands.
OL,13,FShe added: "He was authentic.
OL,15,F"He never tried to be anything other
OL,16,Fthan what he was, and he would tell
OL,17,Fyou the truth about everything and
OL,18,Fthat was him, you knew where you were
OL,19,Fwith him."
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@UO]uD@LOUwD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
