OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784879327
OL,3,C'Feels like he's still here': Tony
OL,4,CIommi honours 'dear friend' Ozzy
OL,6,FThe former X Factor judge, who was
OL,7,Fvisibly emotional in the interview,
OL,8,Falso praised her husband's hometown
OL,9,Ffor hosting "Ozzy Day" ` a series of
OL,10,Fevents commemorating the anniversary
OL,11,Fof his death.
OL,13,FSharon said: "(Birmingham) is the home
OL,14,Fof metal.
OL,16,F"It's Ozzy's home, it's where he was
OL,17,Fborn, what he loved and (Ozzy Day)
OL,18,Fwouldn't work anywhere else.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@VO]uD@NOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
