OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784879327
OL,3,C'Feels like he's still here': Tony
OL,4,CIommi honours 'dear friend' Ozzy
OL,6,F"He loved this city, he loved its
OL,7,Fpeople. He was proud of being a
OL,8,FBrummie and that's it."
OL,10,FSharon added that his final Back To
OL,11,FThe Beginning gig ` which featured
OL,12,Fperformances from Metallica and Guns
OL,13,FN' Roses ` was "beautiful" and
OL,14,F"something my family, my
OL,15,Fgrandchildren, my children will never
OL,16,Fforget".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@WO]uD@POUuD@ZO]vD@AOUxD@GO]
