OL,3,C'Feels like he's still here': Tony
OL,4,CIommi honours 'dear friend' Ozzy
OL,6,FHer youngest daughter, Kelly Osbourne,
OL,7,Fpaid tribute to her father with a
OL,8,Fheartfelt message on Instagram,
OL,9,Fdetailing how "one year ago today, the
OL,10,Fworld changed forever".
OL,12,FThe TV personality, 41, described the
OL,13,Fdeath of her father as "the hardest
OL,14,Fthing I have ever had to endure" and
OL,15,Fsaid her grief "aches every single
OL,16,Fday".
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@VO]uD@XOUvD@`O]wD@POUxD@DO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
