PN,34509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784879327
OL,3,C'Feels like he's still here': Tony
OL,4,CIommi honours 'dear friend' Ozzy
OL,6,FOsbourne also spoke about how she
OL,7,Fwishes her father could see "the
OL,8,Flittle man" her son Sidney is
OL,9,Fbecoming, and hailed the impact Ozzy
OL,10,Fhad on the world.
OL,12,FShe praised her father's working-class
OL,13,Fbackground, and said he "never forgot
OL,14,Fwhat he came from".
OL,16,FThe star ended the emotional tribute
OL,17,Fby saying the past year "has broken me
OL,18,Fin ways I never knew were possible",
OL,19,Fand that she loves and misses Ozzy who
OL,20,F"made me who I am".
