OL,3,C'Feels like he's still here': Tony
OL,4,CIommi honours 'dear friend' Ozzy
OL,6,FBilly Morrison, who is a guitarist for
OL,7,Frocker Billy Idol, also joined in the
OL,8,Ftributes and shared a photo of himself
OL,9,Fwith his close friend and frequent
OL,10,Fcollaborator Ozzy to Instagram.
OL,12,FHe wrote: "I can't believe it's been a
OL,13,Fyear. I miss you mate."
OL,15,FOsbourne was best known for his role
OL,16,Fin Black Sabbath ` which is widely
OL,17,Fcredited with defining and
OL,18,Fpopularising the sound of heavy metal.
OL,26,@tD@KOUuD@WO]
